The '''Duality''', sometimes called '''the Creed''', was a popular and benign [[Tarrack]] religious cult on the planet [[Utharis]]. It was founded on the twin principles of joy and service. Followers could be identified by the [[Tattoo/Legends|tattoos]] on their foreheads.

